<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yạ mn tkẖyr mwt ạlṣlyb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1-yạ mn tkẖyr mwt ạlṣlyb
 ḥbạaⁿ lyʿtq ạ̉sry̱ ạldẖnwb hạ qd ḥmlt ạ̹lyk ṭywby
 wbạlḥnwṭ mlạ̉t jywby 2-hl tṭlbyn rỷys ạlḥyạẗ
 byn ạlqbwr bdnyạ ạlmmạt qd qạm lkn sryʿạaⁿ syạ̉ty
 ftfrḥyn bh yạ ftạty</lyrics>
<author>ḥsny ạlbyṭạr, lḥn ʿrby</author>
